All Implemented Interfaces:
cdx.opencdx.grpc.neural.protector.NeuralProtectorServiceGrpc.AsyncService, io.grpc.BindableService
@GRpcService public class OpenCDXGrpcProtectorController extends cdx.opencdx.grpc.neural.protector.NeuralProtectorServiceGrpc.NeuralProtectorServiceImplBase
gRPC Controller for Protector World.

This controller provides gRPC service implementations for the Neural Protector service, offering functionalities such as anomaly detection, authorization control, privacy protection, real-time monitoring, and user behavior analysis.
